name: Pollen #016 (Camilla)
description: Camilla is a care-free spirit that used to spend her days pranking other nymphs and telling jokes. She often procrastinates when it comes to important tasks, and sometimes needs help. Still, she has a very bright personality and can be a ton of fun. Queen Lamia feels that such a care-free nymph has no place in the Pollen Kingdom and looks forward to extinguishing Camilla with her wicked flames. ~pollenkingdom.com
